### Get Signatures for Address
POST {{rpc_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "signatures",
  "method": "getSignaturesForAddress",
  "params": [
    "{{token_mint}}",
    { "limit": 10 }
  ]
}

